    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/j0rgbv-09/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=612888062963221011&sectionId=612888062996840979)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"gg-1ansgvJm_text","label":"gg-1ansgvJm_text","default":"Crafted in Italy.<br>For the man who appreciates quality"},{"type":"html","id":"ggNngmitjD5_text","label":"ggNngmitjD5_text","default":"Since 1987, our family laboratory has been crafting skincare the Italian way — with patience, precision, and an obsession for quality over quantity"},{"type":"html","id":"gguqPeQwviO_background_desktop_image_src","label":"gguqPeQwviO_background_desktop_image_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/bg.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRm4mpsB6D_text","label":"ggRm4mpsB6D_text","default":"Effortless results.<br>No fuss"},{"type":"html","id":"gg2KNhEqc1H_text","label":"gg2KNhEqc1H_text","default":"In Italy, we have a concept called sprezzatura — the art of making the difficult look effortless. The elegance of a man who cares about how he looks without making a fuss about it.<br><br>This is the philosophy behind SerlinoLab. Products that deliver real results — less wrinkles, firmer skin, a fresher face — without complicated routines. Two minutes a day. That's all it takes"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMTVvezHKQ_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggMTVvezHKQ_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/939c2057-a941-40a9-bf45-7f2ea682d1d2.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsqbb7MCZl_text","label":"ggsqbb7MCZl_text","default":"Small rituals.<br>Big difference"},{"type":"html","id":"ggp6z32qWHU_text","label":"ggp6z32qWHU_text","default":"The Italian art of living — <strong>l'arte di vivere</strong> — is about appreciating small rituals. A good espresso. A sunset over the Mediterranean. A moment of care for yourself.<br>&nbsp;<br>SerlinoLab is that moment. Not a chore. Not a 10-step routine. <strong>A daily ritual that makes you look better and feel better</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMi0ZzJihi_youtubeUrl","label":"ggMi0ZzJihi_youtubeUrl","default":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NfASaHFN1zg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMi0ZzJihi_vimeoUrl","label":"ggMi0ZzJihi_vimeoUrl","default":"https://vimeo.com/1095883398"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMi0ZzJihi_html5Url","label":"ggMi0ZzJihi_html5Url","default":"https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/56c90834-24c9-4b2f-b793-173c1ec67477/21f2c450-85ce-411c-b723-a981f545258a"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTfo6aMwuv_background_desktop_image_src","label":"ggTfo6aMwuv_background_desktop_image_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/bg.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggov1PYiB_N_text","label":"ggov1PYiB_N_text","default":"Crafted on the<br>Italian coast"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUIXanDzl__text","label":"ggUIXanDzl__text","default":"Our family-owned laboratory sits in Campania, just a stone's throw from the Amalfi Coast — the same stretch of Southern Italy that has inspired artists, poets, and craftsmen for generations.&nbsp;Here, our chemists have spent over 30 years perfecting the balance between active ingredients and Italian botanicals. Olive oil from the Marche. Tomato extract from Puglia. Orange from Sicily.&nbsp;No anonymous factories. No outsourcing. Every formula is made here, by people who have dedicated their careers to one thing: skincare that works"},{"type":"html","id":"ggXVbnLBXn__srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggXVbnLBXn__srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/ddce9c4e-19ad-40eb-a5dd-c16ca7a0476f.webp"},{"type":"html","id":"gggo0fs2sYS_text","label":"gggo0fs2sYS_text","default":"What we stand for"},{"type":"html","id":"ggBMnVcdTJw_text","label":"ggBMnVcdTJw_text","default":"<strong>Craftsmanship over marketing. </strong>We'd rather spend money on better ingredients than flashier ads.<br><br><strong>Timelessness over trends.</strong> We don't reformulate every season. We perfect one formula and stand by it.<br><br><strong>Results you can see.</strong> Not promises — proof. 60 days, or your money back"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9ZAxGgp4G_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg9ZAxGgp4G_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/0c358216-c8e0-41ff-989b-cc13c83a9115.webp"}],
